title: API Reference
description: A quick look at all the available API endpoints.

body.raw:
# API Reference

### Endpoint: `/get-data`

- **Method**: `GET`
- **Description**: Fetches the data from the server.

### Endpoint: `/post-data`

- **Method**: `POST`
- **Description**: Submits data to the server.
